<br>
-Monks ~ pet kite, I win (most other meelee except extremely massive ones) oh, and one munk tried to fd when she was low health, it fooled my pet but i nuked her dead np<br>
-SK's ~ no thx, shadowstep, dispell, fear, snare, HT = dead mage<br>
-Other mages ~ depends on how much you/he resists yada yada, and what the pets decide to do<br>
-Wizard ~ if you get your pet on him fast and nuke him down before he can root the pet and start blasting you, you should win...i dueled a low 50s wiz when i was 60 w/o a pet and he crushed me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
