try and keep you blinded, not sure on how much it will <br>
hurt you as a mage.<br>
<br>
Many other casters have tricks that will make fighting<br>
hell on a mage (charms, shadowsteps, fd (makes your pet stop attacking) ect)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I think mages rock the low end game of PvP but get worse<br>
the higher you get (note I have only played a mage to 19: <br>
my experiances are based off watching and fighting higher mages with my other characters) <p>For a good time click <A HREF="http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthescurvydogbuffetfrm1.showMessage?topicID=47.topic">here.</A> <BR><BR>
